src:
ATEEZ wins the award for Best Korean Act at MTV EMA's 2019
03 Nov 2019, 20:28 by Sach007



Ateez have won the award for the Best Korean Act at the MTV EMA's 2019. This is the groups first International Award since their Debut last year.
Congratulations to ATEEZ and Atiny's.
